title: "Tesla shares soar 10% after Morgan Stanley upgrade"
text: "Morgan Stanley upgrades Tesla price target to $400 per share on potential of custom silicon."

title: "Benchmark's Bill Gurley says Meta's Llama AI model has the 'most momentum'"
text: "Gurley said the open-source nature of Meta's product is threatening to other leaders in the AI space."

title: "QCOM Stock Alert: What the Apple Supply Deal Means for Qualcomm"
text: "Qualcomm (NASDAQ: QCOM ) is jumping about 4% on Monday. The positive lift in QCOM stock stems from a new chip supply agreement with consumer tech giant Apple (NASDAQ: AAPL )."
